title: Thursday Dots : Osobor The Great
body_text:
On the eve of an earlier-than-usual gameday for Husky football, it’s the men’s basketball program that has a player receiving major praise. Utah State transfer Great Osobor was listed as the top senior in the nation by analyst Andy Katz and praise like that leads to being the headliner for Dots.
Thursday Dots: Osobor The Great
The UW hoops star is bound to become a household name in college basketball.
We haven’t dove into the upcoming basketball season just yet, but here’s a reminder that you should expect big things from the highly touted (and paid) newcomer.
Perhaps we should stay with basketball before pivoting:
